// Single source of truth for the recruiting-guide program fields.
//
// Both the display page (pages/RecruitingGuide.jsx) and the admin editor render
// from this schema, so the two never drift. Keys match the `profile` JSONB the
// backend stores (generated by scripts/build_recruiting_programs_json.py from the
// PNW Recruiting Guide spreadsheet).
//
// format drives display + editor input type:
//   text       short single-line value (input)
//   multiline  long prose, e.g. coach bio / scholarship notes (textarea)
//   url        rendered as a link; editor uses a url input
//   email      rendered as a mailto link; editor uses an email input

